    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for a practical option. The exterior shows some signs of its age, including a few minor scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, though the paint still holds a decent shine. Inside, the upholstery exhibits some visible wear and a few minor stains from regular use, but all electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it will likely require some routine maintenance like new brake pads and a tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has plenty of life left for a buyer who doesn't mind a bit of character.",
      "price": 19500.0,
